name: podamShouldSupportRecursiveMaps

testSteps.description: When I invoke the factory manufacturing for class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.pdm6.RecursiveMap
Then the pojo uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.pdm6.RecursiveMap@450c77 must be of the type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.pdm6.RecursiveMap
Then the Map should not be null or empty and each element should have key of type class java.lang.String and value of type class uk.co.jemos.podam.test.dto.pdm6.RecursiveMap
